column1: The cost to society will be substantial, the report says. In 2019 alone, it estimates a $290 billion burden from health care, long-term case and hospice combined. Medicare and Medicaid will cover $195 billion of that, with out-of-pocket costs to caregivers reaching $63 billion.
column2: Izindleko zomphakathi zizoba zinkulu, ngokusho kombiko. Ngonyaka wezi-2019 uwodwa, umthwalo wezindleko zezempilo ulinganiselwa kuzigidigidi ezingama-$290, kuhlanganiswa ukugula kwesikhathi eside kanye ne-hospice.  I-Medicare ne-Medicaid izokhokhela izindleko eziyizigidigidi ezingama-$195 walokho, ngezindleko ezikhokhwa ngqo zabanakekeli ezifinyelela kuzigidigidi ezingama-$63.
column3: Lo mbiko uthi, izindleko ziyoba phezulu kakhulu emphakathini. Ngo-2019 wodwa nje, ulinganisela umthwalo ongamabhiliyoni angu-290  amaDola aseMelika wokunakekelwa kwempilo, ukunakekelwa kwesikhathi eside kuhlangene nekhaya labanezifo ezibulalayo. I-Medicare ne-Medicaid bayokhokhokhela amabhiliyoni angu-195 amaDola aseMelika kulezo zindleko, kanti izindleko eziyokhokhelwa ngabanakekeli zingafika kumabhiliyoni angu-63 amaDola aseMelika.

column1: "We are excited that this tool has proven useful to guide local restoration efforts such as the Swan Island Oyster Sanctuary restoration project currently underway in North Carolina," Theuerkauf says. "The beauty of this model and approach is that it can be modified for use in a number of different habitat restoration efforts -- such as mangrove restoration in Florida, where the benefits the habitat provides are different from those of oyster reefs, but similarly very valuable."
column2: "Siyakujabulela ukuthi le nsiza ibonakalile ukuthi izosiza ukuhola ukuvuselelwa kwe-Swan Island Oyster Sanctuary kwasendaweni oqhubekayo njengamanje eNorth Carolina," kusho uTheuerkauf.  "Okuhle ngalolu hlelo nendlelakwenza wukuthi ingalungiselelwa ukusetshenziswa ezindaweni zokuhlala ezahlukene zokubuyisa -- njengokubuyiselwa kwezihlahla ze-mangrove eFlorida, lapho izinzuzo ezihlinzekwa yileyo ndawo zehlukile kunalezo zothunge lwembada, kodwa nazo zibaluleke ngokufanayo."
column3: "Siyajabula ukuthi leli thuluzi selibe usizo ekuqondiseni imizamo yendawo yokubuyisela izinto esimweni njengephrojekthi yokubuyisela i-Swan Island Oyster Sanctuary eqhubekayo njengamanje e-North Carolina," kusho u-Theuerkauf. "Into enhle ngale ndlela ukuthi ingase ishintshwe ukuze isetshenziswe emizamweni eminingana yokubuyisela izindawo zemvelo esimweni – njengokubuyiselwa kwe-mangrove e-Florida, lapho izinzuzo ezilethwa yilezi zindawo zihlukile kulezo zezindawo zama-oyster, kodwa nazo ziwusizo kakhulu."

column1: Last week, the South Bend City Councilman Oliver Davis endorsed former Vice President Joe Biden in what several outlets viewed as a rejection of Mayor Pete. NgoLwesihlanu, uDavis utshele i-Politico ukuthi ukujabulele ukubona umuntu omele i-Indiana kuzwelonke, kodwa uBiden ubonakalise ukuba nesipiliyoni esiningi kunalo muntu oneminyaka engama-37.

NgoLwesihlanu, u-Davis utshele u-Politico ukuthi uyajabula ukubona kukhona umuntu omele i-Indiana enkundleni kazwelonke, kodwa u-Biden unesipiliyoni kakhulu ukudlula lo muntu oneminyaka engu-37 ubudala.

column1: Shellfish collected by children are most easily identified by variety and size, Keegan said. Child foragers tend to be generalists, meaning that they're more likely to collect small shells indiscriminately. This research suggests that small, easy to transport and low-yield mollusks found in high amounts on a site indicate the presence of child foragers, he said.
column2: Ama-shellfish aqoqwa izingane kuvame ukuba lula ukuwahlonza ngokohlobo nobungako, kusho uKeegan. Abadobi abayizingane bavame ukubheka okujwayelekile, okusho ukuthi maningi kakhulu amathuba okuthi baqoqe amagobolondo amancane ngaphandle kokukhetha. Uthe, lolu cwaningo lusho ukuthi izinkovu ezincane, okulula ukuzithutha nezinenzuzo encane ezitholakala ziziningi kakhulu endaweni ziveza ukuthi bekukhona abadobi abayizingane.
column3: Ama-shellfish aqoqwa yizingane abonakala kalula ngokuhlukahluka nangosayizi, kusho u-Keegan. Abaqoqi abayizingane bavame ukuqoqa yonke inhlobo, okusho ukuthi kungenzeka kakhulu ukuba baqoqe namagobolondo amancane. Lolu cwaningo lusikisela ukuthi ama-mollusk amancane, okulula ukuwathutha atholakala ngobuningi kule ndawo, okwakukhomba ukuthi kukhona abaqoqi abayizingane, esho.

column1: The production of sperm -- otherwise known as spermatogenesis -- generates more than 1,000 sperm per second in normal males. This productivity comes, in part, from a special cell type called the spermatogonial stem cell. The staying power of this stem cell has allowed many celebrities, including Robert DeNiro and Pablo Picasso, to father children after the age of 65.
column2: Ukukhiqizwa kwezidoda - okubuye kubizwe ngokuthi i-spermatogenesis - kukhiqiza izidoda ezingaphezu kwe-1,000 ngomzuzu ngamunye emadodeni ngokuvamile. Lokhu kukhiqiza kwenzeka, njengengxenye, kuvela kuhlobo lweseli olukhethekile olubizwa nge-spermatogonial stem cell. Amandla okuhlala ale stem cell avumele ukuthi inqwaba yosaziwayo, okubandakanya uRobert DeNiro noPablo Picasso, babe woyise bezingane beneminyaka engama-65.
column3: Ukukhiqizwa kwesidoda – okwaziwa ngokuthi i-spermatogenesis – kwakha isidoda esingu-1000 ngomzuzwana kwabesilisa abavamile. Ngokwengxenye, lokhu kubangelwa, uhlobo olukhethekile lweseli elibizwa ngokuthi yi-spermatogonial stem cell. Amandla alesi stem cell enze ukuthi izilomo ezithile, ezihlanganisa noRobert DeNiro noPablo Picasso, bakwazi ukuba nabantwana sebedlulile eminyakeni engu-65 ubudala.

column1: Today, those using Planck and cosmic background data to obtain a value for the Hubble constant get a figure of 67.4 plus or minus 0.5. (Bheka "i-A matter of metrics," ngezansi.)
column3: Namuhla, labo abasebenzisa i-Planck kanye ne-cosmic background data ukuze bathole inani le-Hubble elingaguquki bathola isibalo esingu-67.4 plus noma minus 0.5. Ngokuphambene, indlela yalapha inikeza isibalo esingu-73.5 plus noma minus 1.4. La manani amelela amanani amabili angafani esinawo achaza ukwanda kwendawo yonke. (Bheka esithi  "A matter of metrics," ngezansi.)

column1: Unlike cryptocurrencies such as bitcoin, nifties are cryptographic tokens that represent a unique asset or good on the blockchain, are one of a kind, and are not interchangeable. Blockchains can enable gamers to buy and trade interoperable digital collectibles such as skins, dances, and in-game items, helping further fuel a $50 billion-plus annual market1 for virtual goods.
column2: Hhayi njengama-cryptocurrencies anjenge-bitcoin, ama-nifties angamathokheni anezithombe ezi-cryptographic ezimele impahla ehlukile kwi-blockchain, okungavamile, futhi okungasebenziseki ngokushintshanisa. Ama-blockchain angenza abadlali bathenge futhi bahwebe ngezinto ezisebenza ngobuchwepheshe bedijithali ezoqoqekayo njengama-skin, abadansi, nezinto zemidlalo, okusiza ukuqhubeka nokufaka isamba esingaphezu kwezigidigidi ezingu-$50 ezimakethe maqondana nempahla yezobuchwepheshe ephakathi kumakhompyutha.
column3: Ngokungafani nama-cryptocurrencies anjenge-bitcoin, ama-nifties angama-cryptographic token amelela impahla ekhethekile, kuyi-blockchain, ahlukile futhi awashintshaniseki. Ama-blockchain enza abadlali bakwazi ukuthenga nokuhweba izinto eziqoqekayo ezifana nezikhumba, imidanso nezinye izinto zokudlala, okusiza kube nesandla emakethe engenisa u-$50 billion-nangaphezulu ngonyaka ngezimpahla ezingaphatheki.

column1: For one thing, Sondland's testimony explicitly and in detail outlined what he described without reservation as a quid pro quo - one focused on an effort to leverage an official White House meeting to pressure Ukraine to announce new investigations. The claim that "no quid pro quo" ever occurred is the opposite of what Sondland testified. It's just that the quid pro quo that Sondland expressly articulated isn't the one that was the subject of that call.
column2: Ngento eyodwa, ubufakazi bukaSondland ngokusobala buveza imininingwane yalokho okuchazwe ngokusobala ukuthi i-quid pro quo - egxile emizamweni yokusebenzisa umhlangano we-White House osemthethweni ukufakela i-Ukraine ingcindezi yokumemezela ngophenyo olusha. Ukuthi "no quid pro quo" kwake kwenzeka kuphambene nalokho okushiwo uSondland lapho efakaza. Wukuthi nje i-quid pro quo yokuthi uSondland waveza ngokusobala akusikho obekuyisihloko ebesidingidwa kulolo cingo.
column3: Okokuqala, ubufakazi bukaSondland bukubeke ngokucacile nangokuningilizayo lokho akuchaze ngokungagwegwesi ngokuthi ukugezana izandla – okugxile emzamweni wokusebenzisa umhlangano osemthethweni waseWhite House ukucindezela i-Ukraine ukuthi imemezele uphenyo olusha. Ukugomela ngokuthi akukho ‘kugezana izandla’ okuke kwenzeka kuyaphikisana nobufakazi bukaSondland. column1: Anirban Lahiri of India did not have to qualify for his previous two U.S. Opens, and he doesn't want to have to go through it again. Lahiri had no trouble with a 65 at Scioto and a 67 at Brookside, but he could do without the stress. He had never seen either course, opting for what he called "point and shoot."

ULahiri akabanga nenkinga ne-65 at Scioto kanye ne-67 at Brookside, kodwa ubengakwenza ngaphandle kwengcindezi. Ubengakazi azibone zonke izinkundla zokudlala, wakhetha lokhu akubize ngokuthi "point and shoot."
column3: U-Anirban Lahiri waseNdiya akudingekanga ukuthi awakhwalifayele ama-U.S. Open akhe amabili adlule, futhi akafuni ukuphinde akwenze futhi.
